RBK-keeperens klare beskjed: – Det brenner skikkelig nå
02 Nov 2019, 08:00 by Ole K. Sagbakken
André Hansen mener kampene mot Molde og Sporting viser at spillergruppa tror på «prosjekt Horneland».

Strømsgodset – Rosenborg 3–3
text:
RBK keeper's clear message: - It's burning really well now
02 Nov 2019, 08:00 by Ole K. Sagbakken
André Hansen believes the matches against Molde and Sporting show that the player group believes in "project Horneland".

Power goods - Rosenborg 3–3
